Quest Information


Prequest:
Jasper

Given By: Edwin the ArcaneArchitect

Giver Location: Kondha Desert
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Talk to Duran DuneFather}

(in Sands of Time Cave)


Hand In: Duran DuneFather

Reward:

75
7,750


Leads to:

Stopping the Sand of Time

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.
